<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1943-10-14T23:59:59-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1943-10-14T00:00:00-05:00" n="42" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d42">
                        <note rend="inline" type="source"><persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName> Papers: Telegram</note>
                        <head><hi rend="italic">President <persName corresp="#p_RFD1" type="from">Roosevelt</persName> to Marshal <persName corresp="#p_SIV1" type="to">Stalin</persName></hi><note n="1" xml:id="d42fn1">Sent
                                to the United States Naval Attach, Moscow, via Navy
                            channels.</note></head>
                        <opener>
                            <seg rendition="#left"><hi rend="smallcaps">secret</hi>
                                <lb/>
                                <hi rend="smallcaps">operational priority</hi></seg>
                            <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi></placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-10-14">14 October 1943</date>.</dateline>
                        </opener>
                        <p>Personal and secret from President <persName corresp="#p_RFD1">Roosevelt</persName> to Marshal <persName corresp="#p_SIV1">Stalin</persName>.</p>
                        <p>The Secretary of State and his Staff are well on their way to Moscow but
                            it seems doubtful at this time that they will be able to get there
                            before the seventeenth. I will let you know of their progress.</p>
                        <pb facs="0123" n="31" xml:id="pg_31"/>
                        <p>I am much disturbed in regard to the location of the other meeting but I
                            will send you this problem in another message.<note n="2" xml:id="d42fn2"><hi rend="italic">Infra</hi>.</note></p>
                        <closer><signed><persName corresp="#p_RFD1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Roosevelt</hi></persName></signed></closer>
                    </div>
                    </body></text></TEI>